  connected --> 1: [Q](STREAM) [H3](SETTINGS,RESERVED) / ACK

  connected --> 2: [Q](STREAM,STREAM) [H3](PRIORITY_UPDATE) [H3](HEADERS) / ACK,STREAM(0)[HEADERS],STREAM(0)[None]

  connected --> 3: [Q](ACK) / CLOSE

